org.wildfly.swarm.container.config

Class ConfigViewImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wildfly.swarm.container.config.ConfigViewImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigView, StageConfig

    public class ConfigViewImpl
extends Object
implements ConfigView
    A view of merged/activated configurations.

    If an explicit properties object is provided (withProperties(Properties), then the System properties will be completely ignored. If not, then System properties will be inspected, and any non-property based configuration will be reflect back into the live and active System properties.

    Author:
    Bob McWhirter
